l communications. It is argued that independence (and quality of life for older adults) is linked to technology that enables interdependence, and specifically technology that supports social communication between key roles including residents, caregivers, and family members.<\\/jats:p>\",\"DOI\":\"10.3390\\/s19030485\",\"type\":\"journal-article\",\"created\":{\"date-parts\":[[2019,1,24]],\"date-time\":\"2019-01-24T16:12:48Z\",\"timestamp\":1548346368000},\"page\":\"485\",\"source\":\"Crossref\",\"is-referenced-by-count\":5,\"title\":\"IoT\\/Sensor-Based Infrastructures Promoting a Sense of Home, Independent Living, Comfort and Wellness\",\"prefix\":\"10.3390\",\"volume\":\"19\",\"author\":[{\"given\":\"Joan\",\"family\":\"Cahill\",\"sequence\":\"first\",\"affiliation\":[]},{\"given\":\"Raul\",\"family\":\"Portales\",\"sequence\":\"additional\",\"affiliation\":[]},{\"given\":\"Sean\",\"family\":\"McLoughin\",\"sequence\":\"additional\",\"affiliation\":[]},{\"ORCID\":\"http:\\/\\/orcid.org\\/0000-0001-5905-6090\",\"authenticated-orcid\":false,\"given\":\"Nithia\",\"family\":\"Nagan\",\"sequence\":\"additional\",\"affiliation\":[]},{\"given\":\"Braden\",\"family\":\"Henrichs\",\"sequence\":\"additional\",\"affiliation\":[]},{\"given\":\"Sean\",\"family\":\"Wetherall\",\"sequence\":\"additional\",\"affiliation\":[]}],\"member\":\"1968\",\"published-online\":{\"date-parts\":[[2019,1,24]]},\"reference\":[{\"key\":\"ref1\",\"series-title\":\"True Visions: The Emergence of Ambient Intelligence\",\"author\":\"Aarts\",\"year\":\"2008\"},{\"key\":\"ref2\",\"doi-asserted-by\":\"publisher\",\"DOI\":\"10.1145\\/1978802.1978815\"},{\"key\":\"ref3\",\"doi-asserted-by\":\"publisher\",\"DOI\":\"10.1016\\/j.pmcj.2009.04.001\"},{\"key\":\"ref4\",\"unstructured\":\"Ageing Well in the Digital Worldwww.aal-europe.eu\"},{\"key\":\"ref5\",\"doi-asserted-by\":\"publisher\",\"DOI\":\"10.1109\\/JBHI.2012.2234129\"},{\"key\":\"ref6\",\"doi-asserted-by\":\"publisher\",\"DOI\":\"10.1108\\/IntR-0